This is a Play 2.2 exmple application demonstrating integration of the controller with PicoContainer. 

This does not integrate all the Pico-Web scoping capabilities (yet)
=====================================================================================================

Requirements: 
	Scala 2.1.0
	http://scala-lang.org/
	
	
	Play 2.2.0 
	http://www.playframework.com/download

Once you have the requirements installed you can run by typing:

play run		or 		play debug run

Then open your browsr to http://localhost:9000/
